description:
QNAP QuDedup Extract Tool helps restore deduplicated .qdff

QNAP QuDedup Extract Tool helps restore deduplicated .qdff (QNAP deduplication file format) files to their normal status. Windows速, Mac速 and Linux速 (Ubuntu速) users can install it on their computers to restore .qdff files downloaded from a remote NAS or the cloud. The QuDedup Extract Tool also allows users to preview and select files before restoring them, while the granular recovery function allows for restoring specific folders or individual files, greatly improving the convenience and efficiency to access backed-up .qdff files.
[Fixed Issues]
- Fixed an issue where the application would sometimes fail to restore files from a .qdff file.
